snippet.title: MahaShivRatri 2025 – Livestream with Sadhguru | 26 Feb, 6 PM - 27 Feb, 6 AM IST
snippet.description:
Celebrate Mahashivratri 2025 with Sadhguru on 26 February 2025, starting at 6 PM IST/12:30 PM GMT.

On Mahashivratri night, there is a powerful natural upsurge of energy in the human system. It is enormously beneficial for one’s physical and spiritual wellbeing to stay awake and aware in a vertical posture throughout the night.

This year, Sadhguru will be offering initiation into the powerful Mahamantra (Aum Namah Shivaya) at midnight.

This Mahashivratri, contribute towards supporting Mahashivratri activities and Maha Annadanam (the sacred offering of food) to thousands of devotees. Your contribution, small or large, will make a big difference! Donate Now: https://sadhguru.co/annam

Join Sadhguru for the powerful Pancha Bhuta Kriya online on the auspicious night of Mahashivratri. Experience this powerful process that brings the body and mind to a vibrant state of health and wellbeing by purifying the five elements within the human system.

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Kollagottinadhiro -Lyrical|Hari Hara Veera Mallu|PSPK|Nidhhi|MM Keeravaani |AM Rathnam|Jyothi Krisna
snippet.description:
Experience our folksy foot-tapping number " Kollagottinadhiro" from 'Hari Hara Veera Mallu (Telugu)'  🎶🔥 Featuring PSPK, Nidhhi Agerwal, and Bobby Deol, this foot-tapping track is composed by Oscar winner MM Keeravaani and directed by Jyothi Krisna & Krish Jagarlamudi.

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Telugu, Subscribe on the below link
https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Song Details : 
Song Name: Kollagottinadhiro
Music Director: M. M. Keeravaani 
Lyricist: Chandrabose 
Singers: Mangli, Rahul Sipligunj , Ramya Behara, Yamini Ghantasala. 
Chorus : Lokeshwar Edara, Sai Charan, Arun kaundinya, Airaa Udupi , Lipsika Bhashyam, Vaish
Programmed, Mixed and Mastered by : Jeevan Babu 
Recording Studio: JB Studios 
Co-ordinator: A N Basha

Lyrics : 
Kora Kora Meesalatho, Kodama Kodama Adugulatho 
Kontey Kontey Chenukulatho, Kolimilanti Magatimitho Sarasara Vacchinaadu Chicchara Pidugantivaadu 
Edo Edo Thalachinaadu Evvarino Vethikinaadu 
Evaranta… Evaranta… Evarevaranta
Evaranta Evaranta Evarevarevarevaranta

Kondapalli Endi Bomma 
Kola Kallatho Chusindamma Teeyateeyani Teynelakomma
Teeyani Teraley Teesindamma
Vajrala Jilugulunna 
Rathnala Yelugulunna Kempulla Ompulunna Mohareela Merupulunna
Naa Paidi Gundeylona Edi Puttinchi 
Mariginchi Mariginchi Kariginchi Kariginchi

Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro
Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Ayyayyayyo….…Aa Chinnadi 
Inkemi Chesindayyo. 
Ayyayyayyo...Aa Kurradi Aa Mantram Esindayyo..

Kannulaloni Kaatuka Megham 
Seekati Naapai Silikindey 
Maatalathoney Melikeysindi 
Marmam Edo Daasindey
Aadavaallu Manasu Adavilantidani 
Eragani Santodiva
Antha Amayakudiva
Padusupilla Teeru Pattusikkadani Pasigattalenodiva 
Votti Shontikommuva…
Letha Ennapoosava…..
Are Meesala Roshala Monaganni Pattesi 
Pasivanni Chesesi Pasaredo Poosesi…
Kollagottinaadiro
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro….
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Oopiriloni Aaviripavanaaley 
Viriviga Lekhaley Visireney
Uppena Laaga Pongey Pourushamey 
Sogasuku Sankela Veseyney
Cheekuchintha Leni Vaadi Chittam Dochavey Parahushaar Poragadni Paagal Chesavey Daaredayina Davvedayina Needayi Untaney Pereydaina Teeredayina Penimiti Antaney Addeddedde….
Kollagottinaadiro….
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro Mulleygattinaadiro…

snippet.title: The Bhootnii - Announcement | Sanjay D, Mouni R, Sunny, Palak, Nick | Sidhaant S | Deepak M | 18 Apr
snippet.description:
Get ready for a rollercoaster of horror, romance, and comedy like never before! Presenting "The Bhootnii", where love, laughter and supernatural thrills come together in the most unexpected way! 👻💘🤣

Starring the legendary Sanjay Dutt, the stunning Mouni Roy, the charming Sunny Singh, the talented Palak Tiwari, the hilarious Asif Khan, and the quirky BeYounik, this film is packed with spine-tingling moments, hilarious twists, and a whole lot of romance! 💀❤️✨

🎬The Bhootnii is set to hit theaters on 18th April 2025.

Credits : 
⭐ cast : Sanjay Dutt, Mouni Roy, Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Asif Khan, BeYounik & Others
Written & Directed by : Sidhaant Sachdev
Produced by : Deepak Mukut & Sanjay Dutt
Co-Produced by : Hunar Mukut & Maanayata Dutt
Associate Producer : Johari Tailor
DOP : Santosh Thundiyil ISC
Editor : Bunty Nagi 
Screenplay & Dialogue : Vankush Arora & Sidhaant Sachdev
Production Design : Dipankar Das Gupta & Sunayana Paradkar (Teena)
Sound Design : Kunal Mehta & Parikshit Lalwani (Creative Sound Design)
BG Music :  Amar Mohile
Choreographer : Ganesh Acharya 
Executive Producer: Mehboob Ansari & Pradeep Singh
Action : Real Satish
Costume Designer- Priyanka Mundada 
Sanjay Dutt’s Costume- Anna Singh & Navin Shetty
VFX : Redifine 
VFX Supervisor - Govardhan Vigraham
Associate Director : Rishabh Rishi Kumar 
Music : ICONYK, Shabbir Ahmed, Mukund Suryawanshi (Jam8)
Creative Director : Manoj Tiwari & Rishi Anand
CEO (TDM) : Gaurav Dubey
CEO & Business Head (SRE) : Shailendra Mandowara 
Digital Mrkt. Manager (SRE) : Ajay S Singh
Production Team (SRE) : Lucky Tomar, Shivam Rao
Banner : Soham Rockstar Entertainment & Three Dimension Motion Pictures

• Rock Salt(सेंधा नमक) - Some

• Grated Ginger (अदरक) - 1 Tbsp

• Cottage Cheese/Paneer (पनीर) -  100 Gram
• Salt (नमक) - 1/2 Tsp
• Black Pepper Powder (काली मिर्च) - 1/2 Tsp
• Green Chili (हरी मिर्च) - 2-3
• Oil/Ghee (तेल/घी) - For Frying

For Serving:
• Whisked Curd (फेंटा हुआ दही)
• Green Chutney (हरी चटनी)
• Sweet Chutney (मीठी चटनी)
• Pomagranate Seeds (अनार के दाने)
• Coriander leaves (धनिया पत्ती)
• Roasted Cumin Powder (जीरा पाउडर)

snippet.title: Son of Sreenivasan Roast | Love Under Construction | Dhyan | Neeraj | Aju | Vishnu | Feb 28th
snippet.description:
Brace yourselves for the ultimate roast interview! Dhyan Sreenivasan takes the hot seat as the host of Son of Sreenivasan Roast, where he gets hilariously grilled alongside his guests—Neeraj Madhav, Aju Varghese, and Vishnu Raghav. Expect witty comebacks, savage burns, and non-stop laughter as they dish out jokes, share behind-the-scenes fun, and promote their upcoming web series Love Under Construction, streaming on JioHotstar from February 28.

Don't miss this riotous episode full of fun, banter, and unexpected twists!

Production Crew Details 

Directed by - Neethu Naduvathettu
Curated & Produced by - Reel Tribe 
Executive Producers - Vivek Viswanath, Binu Balan 
Associate Director's - Hrishikesh MA, Shelvin James, Arjun V R
Production Controller  - Ajay KS
Production Assistants  - Nived V Das, Aswin Anil
Production Designs - Devadath MS, Raveena N
Set Production - Bhagyanath Vishwanath

Kaaki Sattai is a 2015 Indian Tamil-language action thriller film co-written and directed by R. S. Durai Senthilkumar and produced by Dhanush, their second collaboration after Ethir Neechal (2013). The film stars Sivakarthikeyan and Sri Divya, Vijay Raaz and Prabhu. The film's music was composed by Anirudh Ravichander. The story revolves around police constable Mathimaran who wants to prove himself as a true, powerful cop by finding ways to solve issues of corruption in the law and order system in the department of police.

Puthiya Thalaimurai TV (Tamil: புதிய தலைமுறை டிவி) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on August 24, 2011. Puthiya Thalaimurai TV (Tamil: புதிய தலைமுறை டிவி) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on August 24, 2011. Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favor or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organization or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.
 
Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of weekend programmes.
 
The channel is promoted by Chennai based New Gen Media Corporation. The company also publishes popular Tamil magazines - Puthiya Thalaimurai and Kalvi.

Judwaa is the story of twin girls who share the same face but have contrasting personalities and destinies. One is gentle and reserved, while the other is bold and fearless. As fate weaves unexpected twists, their lives take dramatic turns. Starring Aina Asif in a dual role, this gripping drama explores identity, destiny, and the power of choice.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Bhide Ka Surprise | Bhide dega Jhatka | Gokuldham Society

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi

Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku

Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: Shiv Aarti Anuradha Paudwal | Jai Shiv Omkara | Shiv Aarti | Shiv Ji Ki Aarti | ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा
snippet.description:
Shiv Aarti Anuradha Paudwal | Jai Shiv Omkara | Shiv Aarti | Shiv Ji Ki Aarti | ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा
Song - Jai Shiv Omkara
Singer - Anuradha Paudwal
Music Director: Dr. Sanjayraj Gaurinandan (SRG)
Lyrics: Traditional

अपने दिन को सकारात्मक ऊर्जा से भरने के लिए सब्सक्राइब कीजिये और अपने मित्र परिवार के साथ शेर कीजिये| 
🔔 SUBSCRIBE NOW: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ShemarooBhakti

!! ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा की आरती - Om Jai Shiv Omkara Lyrics in Hindi !!
.
ओम जय शिव ओंकारा, स्वामी जय शिव ओंकारा।
ब्रह्मा, विष्णु, सदाशिव, अर्द्धांगी धारा॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
एकानन चतुरानन पञ्चानन राजे।
हंसासन गरूड़ासन वृषवाहन साजे॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
दो भुज चार चतुर्भुज दसभुज अति सोहे।
त्रिगुण रूप निरखत त्रिभुवन जन मोहे॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
अक्षमाला वनमाला मुण्डमालाधारी।
त्रिपुरारी कंसारी कर माला धारी॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
श्वेताम्बर पीताम्बर बाघंबर अंगे।
सनकादिक गरुड़ादिक भूतादिक संगे॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
कर के मध्य कमण्डल चक्र त्रिशूलधारी।
जगकर्ता जगभर्ता जगसंहारकर्ता॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
ब्रह्मा विष्णु सदाशिव जानत अविवेका।
प्रणवाक्षर के मध्ये ये तीनों एका॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
पर्वत सोहैं पार्वती, शंकर कैलासा।
भांग धतूरे का भोजन, भस्मी में वासा॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
जटा में गंग बहत है, गल मुण्डन माला।
शेष नाग लिपटावत, ओढ़त मृगछाला॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
काशी में विराजे विश्वनाथ, नन्दी ब्रह्मचारी।
नित उठ दर्शन पावत, महिमा अति भारी॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
त्रिगुणस्वामी जी की आरति जो कोइ नर गावे।
कहत शिवानन्द स्वामी, मनवान्छित फल पावे॥
ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥ स्वामी ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥

Shiv Aarti & Bhajans

https://youtu.be/Eef79MK4bSA
https://youtu.be/KjuxFnWdYpk
https://youtu.be/FkqhOr_U90E
https://youtu.be/JN_EvHnCpvY

snippet.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
snippet.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao 😋

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! 😅

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" 🤷‍♀️ From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments – we want to hear all the juicy details! 😉 Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

Don't forget to follow us for more fun content!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FilterCopy/

Bhay na goda na hathi

Aaj mujhe nachan de

Aaj mujhe nachan de..

snippet.description:
Bhide Bana Detactive | Bhide Ka Naya Mission |

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs PAK: Pakistan की India के आगे हार, Pakistani Fan ने की भयंकर बेइज़्ज़ती
snippet.description:
Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs PAK: Pakistan की India के आगे हार, Pakistani Fan ने की भयंकर बेइज़्ज़ती 

#championstrophy2025 #indiavspakistan #indvspak   

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ जीत के बाद पाकिस्तान के खिलाफ भी टीम इंडिया ने 6 विकेट से जीत हासिल की. इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में जहां ख़ुशी की लहर है, वहां पाकिस्तानी क्रिकेट फैंस को ये डर है कि पाकिस्तान चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी से लगभग बाहर हो चुकी है. भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं पाकिस्तानी फैंस?भारत के लिए जीत के हीरो बने विराट कोहली जिन्होंने शानदार शतक ठोका. पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस इंडियन क्रिकेट टीम के क्यों हुए मुरीद? पाकिस्तानी टीम के स्टार खिलाड़ी बाबर आज़म, हारिस रउफ, शाहीन अफरीदी, मोहम्मद रिज़वान पर क्यों फूटा पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस का गुस्सा? बहुचर्चित पाकिस्तानी गेंदबाज़ी क्यों हुई शुबमन गिल, श्रेयस अय्यर, विराट, रोहित शर्मा के आगे फेल? क्या हुआ जब इंडिया बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के बाद दुबई में इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस और पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस ने मिलकर किया पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को ट्रोल और रोस्ट, जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच की ये खास वीडियो. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started from February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. After the victory against Bangladesh, Team India also won against Pakistan by 6 wickets. While there is a wave of happiness among Indian cricket fans, Pakistani cricket fans are afraid that Pakistan is almost out of the Champions Trophy. How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ जीत के बाद पाकिस्तान के खिलाफ भी टीम इंडिया ने 6 विकेट से जीत हासिल की. इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में जहां ख़ुशी की लहर है, वहां पाकिस्तानी क्रिकेट फैंस को ये डर है कि पाकिस्तान चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी से लगभग बाहर हो चुकी है. भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं पाकिस्तानी फैंस?भारत के लिए जीत के हीरो बने विराट कोहली जिन्होंने शानदार शतक ठोका. पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस इंडियन क्रिकेट टीम के क्यों हुए मुरीद? पाकिस्तानी टीम के स्टार खिलाड़ी बाबर आज़म, हारिस रउफ, शाहीन अफरीदी, मोहम्मद रिज़वान पर क्यों फूटा पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस का गुस्सा? बहुचर्चित पाकिस्तानी गेंदबाज़ी क्यों हुई शुबमन गिल, श्रेयस अय्यर, विराट, रोहित शर्मा के आगे फेल? क्या हुआ जब इंडिया बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के बाद दुबई में इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस और पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस ने मिलकर किया पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को ट्रोल और रोस्ट, जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच की ये खास वीडियो. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started from February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. After the victory against Bangladesh, Team India also won against Pakistan by 6 wickets. While there is a wave of happiness among Indian cricket fans, Pakistani cricket fans are afraid that Pakistan is almost out of the Champions Trophy. How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Bajjo Episode 65 - [Eng Sub] - Javeria Saud - Arez Ahmed - Suqaynah Khan - 26th February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Bajjo is a heartfelt family drama that blends light-hearted moments with emotional turbulence. It portrays the struggles and conflicts of a middle-class household, where differences and arguments often take center stage.
Musarrat, fondly called Bajjo, is the eldest sibling, known for her sharp tongue and bitter demeanor. Her unmarried status fuels her frustration, leading to threats of drastic actions if anyone weds before her. This turmoil unsettles the entire family, but when a proposal finally comes her way, it brings its own set of challenges.
Will Bajjo ever find her match? Can her attitude change, or will it continue to cause problems for her family? Is her family’s patience running out, or will they stand by her despite her flaws? Can Bajjo overcome her struggles?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mazhar Moin
Writer: Javeria Saud

Cast:

snippet.title: Mann Mast Malang Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 23rd February 2025
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 23rd February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Ali Faizan
Writer: Nooran Makhdoom

Cast:
Danish Taimoor as Kabir 
Sahar Hashmi as Riya 
Saba Hamid as Mah Bina 
Uzma Hassan as Asma 
Adnan Samad as Sikandar 
Hiba Ali Khan as Wafa 
Nayyer Ejaz as Chacha 
Dodi Khan as Wajid 
Ramiz Siddiqui as Rameez 
Yasir Alam as Yasir 
Kamran Jeelani as Mubeen
Sheherzade Noor Peerzada as Kashaf 
Maha Hasan as Minha  
Faisal Bali as Bhola 
Sharif Baloch as Inspector
Harmain Ghalib as Kabir (young) 
Aayat Arif as Riya (young)

#MannMastMalang
#DanishTaimoor
